<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.3">
<l>maṟṟumōr teyva muḷateṉ ṟiruppārō</l>
<l>ṭuṟṟilē ṉuṟṟatu muṉṉaṭi yārkkaṭimai</l>
<l>maṟṟellām pēcilum niṉtiru veṭṭeḻuttum</l>
<l>kaṟṟunāṉ kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I will not join with those who would say there is another god;</l>
<l>What [I] will join is service to your servants,</l>
<l>I, having practiced your eight divine letters,</l>
<l>Even if [I] said all other things, lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
